cn.domob.android.ads
接口 DomobInterstitialAdListener

public interface DomobInterstitialAdListener

Domob插屏广告监听器类。

通过该监听器类可以实现插屏广告各种状态的回调。

方法摘要
 void onInterstitialAdDismiss()
          插屏广告关闭
 void onInterstitialAdFailed()
          插屏广告请求失败
 void onInterstitialAdPresent()
          插屏广告开始显示
 void onInterstitialAdReady()
          插屏广告请求成功
 void onLandingPageClose()
          插屏广告点击后关闭LandingPage
 void onLandingPageOpen()
          插屏广告点击后打开LandingPage
